		{
			"id": "xaji0y6d",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## INF-01 Provision base VMs\n\nSet up virtual machines and networking.",
			"x": 80,
			"y": 1340,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "6"
		},
		{
			"id": "pbhsahxt",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## INF-02 Configure DNS and load balancer\n\nRegister domains, set up LB rules.",
			"x": 80,
			"y": 1590,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "6"
		},
		{
			"id": "hv3a3zmf",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## INF-03 Bootstrap secrets manager\n\nVault init, policies, auth backends.",
			"x": 785,
			"y": 1340,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "6"
		},
		{
			"id": "8mdd4v30",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## BE-01 Scaffold API service\n\nGenerate OpenAPI stubs, wire DI.",
			"x": 1490,
			"y": 1340,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "6"
		},
		{
			"id": "t9nt3w5u",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## BE-02 Implement auth endpoints\n\nJWT issue, refresh, revoke flows.",
			"x": 2195,
			"y": 1340,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "6"
		},
		{
			"id": "legend",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## Legend\n🔴 **Red** = To Do (ready)\n⬛ **Gray** = Blocked\n🟠 **Orange** = Doing\n🔵 **Cyan** = Ready to review\n🟢 **Green** = Done\n🟣 **Purple** = Proposed by agent",
			"x": -540,
			"y": -310,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 230,
			"color": "6"
		},
		{
			"id": "canvas-warnings",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## Warnings\n✓ None",
			"x": -540,
			"y": -530,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 200,
			"color": "3"
		},
		{
			"id": "canvas-errors",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## Errors\n✓ None",
			"x": -540,
			"y": -750,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 200,
			"color": "1"
		},
		{
			"id": "zbikcidk",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## BE-03 Implement data CRUD\n\nREST handlers with DB transactions.",
			"x": 2195,
			"y": 1590,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "6"
		},
		{
			"id": "wnnhj7xv",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## BE-04 Add rate limiting & caching\n\nRedis-backed throttle + cache layer.",
			"x": 2900,
			"y": 1340,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "6"
		},
		{
			"id": "g0fn9xuy",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## BE-05 Write integration tests\n\nCover all happy and error paths.",
			"x": 3605,
			"y": 1340,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "6"
		},
		{
			"id": "41ibljh7",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## FE-01 Bootstrap SPA shell\n\nVite + React + router setup.",
			"x": 1490,
			"y": 1970,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "6"
		},
		{
			"id": "5lxo6qji",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## FE-02 Build auth UI\n\nLogin, logout, token refresh UI.",
			"x": 2195,
			"y": 1970,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "6"
		},
		{
			"id": "ujv6oh9s",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## FE-03 Build data dashboard\n\nTables, charts, filter controls.",
			"x": 2900,
			"y": 1970,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "6"
		},
		{
			"id": "dbdw2pcn",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## FE-04 Cross-browser testing\n\nPlaywright suite on Chrome/FF/Safari.",
			"x": 3605,
			"y": 1970,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "6"
		},
		{
			"id": "9t84azyt",
